Seriously, well I have never been really scared by a movie after the age of 12, I have seen some movies that gave me ideas that I was able to develop into something spooky (scary by association?).<br>
<br>
<br>
If ya wanna be SUPER EVIL (!) find someone who is afraid of clowns (and I mean heavy duty phobia here), liquor them up to the point that they pass out.  By the time they awaken, you want to have them strapped to a chair exactly three feet away from a Big Screen television, just as the movie &quot;Killer Klowns From Outer Space&quot; (yes, clowns is intentionally mispelled in the title) begins playing.  For added evil enjoyment, wait for them to retreat to their &quot;safe spot&quot; (usually indicated by soft humming and rocking back and forth) then force a tab of acid down there throat.......<br>
